<P><GAP DESC="illegible" EXTENT="1 span"> &s;peaker and <GAP DESC="illegible" EXTENT="1 word"> do &s;o too, till God &amp; Authority &s;top their mouths, <HI>Quod fax it Dens.</HI> <GAP DESC="blank"> Imprimatur <HI>Ja: Cranford,</HI> Sept. 2. 1646. <HI>FINIS.</HI></P>
